text:
I was recommended Miss Hosting by a friend who said they were really good, I haven't been let down, from the start their support have been nothing but outstanding! Can't recommend them enough.
Extremely prompt customer service, highly technical staff. World defiantly recommend to anyone.
Thank you so much Pratik Zambare and Kevin for been so mind service (5 stars) when I have need help with a fast response.
